('mauricedawson','{\"day\":1,\"month\":1,\"year\":2011}','{\"day\":1,\"month\":5,\"year\":2011}','Unmanned Air System (UAS) Project for PROJ660 Course','This course introduced students to project cost estimation techniques. Students learned how to adjust cost estimates based on resource availability and project risk, and evaluate quality of cost estimates prepared by others.  Students learned the earned-value management technique.   Students use software package(s) to estimate costs.  The associated project was to build an Unmanned Air System (UAS), website, document, and capture all costs associated with weekly cost reports.  This course was designed to reflect a real defense project using principles of Earned Value Management (EVM) in aerospace setting.',NULL,'1','1','2011','1','5','2011'),
